channel.title: [OldSchool] Deob With XTEA Dumper
channel.description:
I made a quick deob made it load runescape, and then added a landscape file dumper to it. Decided to release it obviously.
[url=https://mega.co.nz/#!LVgUQDoI!Ua3Ox1fxidWYUogvJt6WXQ8-wBEcqtSS8vQs8kyqJFw]https://mega.co.nz/#!LVgUQDoI!Ua3Ox1fxidWYUogvJt6WXQ8-wBEcqtSS8vQs8kyqJFw[/url]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/zX2K6MZ.png[/img]
Just dumps to .txt file cause I was lazy and just wanted to get it to work properly.
They use semi new obfuscation so there is a lot of duplicate methods, yes the deob could be much cleaner, but I didn't run all of my bytecode transformers on the original application, because I wanted to make sure I simply had a working dumper client.
